plot: Effy is unhappy when she sees that everybody seems to find Katie more popular than herself, even Freddie. Katie is even more popular when she invites everybody to a party - except Cook, who gate-crashes it anyway. At the party Effy gets back her status as the focus of attention when she brings some magic mushrooms, but she ends up taking a bad trip and fighting with Katie, whom she puts into hospital. She tries to visit her but is rejected and wakes up in a stolen car driven by Cook.—don @ minifie-1
